#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:24 baa824dda57b465a84c0ff89f036f144
msgid "Diagram of the PictoStick buttons"
msgstr "Diagram van de PictoStick-knoppen"

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:28 6d46307471a4429697a21540250fa64d
msgid "**Button A (Side Button)**: Use this to scroll **up** through your activities. This is also the main power button."
msgstr "**Knop A (Zijknop)**: Gebruik deze om **omhoog** door uw activiteiten te scrollen. Dit is ook de hoofd-aan/uit-knop."

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:29 24daa4c580134506a48438b2710becad
msgid "**Button B (Side Button)**: Use this to scroll **down** through your activities."
msgstr "**Knop B (Zijknop)**: Gebruik deze om **omlaag** door uw activiteiten te scrollen."

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:30 d9417c7a5adf46f2a82baa3c0d8ebb89
msgid "**Button C (Large M5 Button)**: Press this to mark an activity as **done**."
msgstr "**Knop C (Grote M5-knop)**: Druk hierop om een activiteit als **klaar** te markeren."

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:33 0e4806bd98fc4a14ab4a4a29f919396d
msgid "Waking Up the Device"
msgstr "Het Apparaat Activeren"

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:34 c55c85031b8345ffa33d2b08267a0c69
msgid "To save battery, the screen will automatically turn off after a few seconds. This is sleep mode."
msgstr "Om de batterij te sparen, wordt het scherm na enkele seconden automatisch uitgeschakeld. Dit is de slaapstand."

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:36 6f661b09a9734bc190b38859f66d4b27
msgid "**To wake the device up**: Briefly press **Button A**. The screen will light up, showing your current activity."
msgstr "**Om het apparaat te activeren**: Druk kort op **Knop A**. Het scherm licht op en toont uw huidige activiteit."

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:39 587aff00cc1a41509bbcec07433cff63
msgid "The Main Screen"
msgstr "Het Hoofdscherm"

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:40 a8433bc700674fdf8468a1ee740000c9
msgid "The screen shows you everything you need to know for your day."
msgstr "Het scherm toont u alles wat u moet weten voor uw dag."

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:42 422c705dbf7e437ab71c762d5a91d3d1
msgid "The main screen of the PictoStick"
msgstr "Het hoofdscherm van de PictoStick"

#: ../../users/howto_use.rst:46 db065a518fc3489bae05e53466ae065c
msgid "**Your Name**: At the very top, you will see your name."
